i/Louis_de_Sacy" title="Louis de Sacy">Louis de Sacy</a></div><div class="next_bloc"><a href="/wiki/Jean-Baptiste_Vivien_de_Châteaubrun" title="Jean-Baptiste Vivien de Châteaubrun">Jean-Baptiste Vivien de Châteaubrun</a></div></th></tr><tr style="background-color:#C9D9FF;padding:4px;text-align:center;color:#000000"><th colspan="2" style="background-color:#C9D9FF;padding:4px;text-align:center;color:#000000"><a href="/wiki/Juge" title="Juge">Juge</a></th></tr></tbody></table><table><caption style="color:#FFFFFF;text-align:center;background-color:#4C6099">Titre de noblesse</caption><tbody><tr style="background-color:#C9D9FF;padding:4px;text-align:center;color:#000000"><th colspan="2" style="background-color:#C9D9FF;padding:4px;text-align:center;color:#000000"><a href="/wiki/Baron_(noblesse)" title="Baron (noblesse)">Baron</a></th></tr></tbody></table><table><caption style="color:#FFFFFF;text-align:center;background-color:#4C6099">Biographie</caption><tbody><tr class=""><th scope="row">Naissance</th><td class=""><div>
